package SRP

// ? 1  Single Responsibility Principle (SRP)

A class should have only one reason to change ,A class should have only one job
A class should have only one responsibility

there is a class level and method level
class level: a class should have only one reason to change (not more than one responsibility like class banck have a responsibility to manage the account and also to manage the customer # not good)
method level: a method should have only one reason to change (not more than one responsibility like method addCustomer have a responsibility to add customer and also to send email # not good)


